        <div class="usage-note">
            <h3>=€ Usage Examples</h3>
            <p><strong>Get Pikachu's data:</strong></p>
            <div class="example">GET https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokemon/pikachu</div>
            <div class="example">GET https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokemon/25</div>
            
            <p><strong>Get all Fire-type moves:</strong></p>
            <div class="example">GET https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/type/fire</div>
            
            <p><strong>Get evolution chain:</strong></p>
            <div class="example">GET https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/evolution-chain/1</div>
            
            <p><strong>=Ý Notes:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>All endpoints support both ID numbers and names</li>
                <li>Responses are paginated with 20 items per page by default</li>
                <li>No API key required - completely free to use</li>
                <li>CORS enabled for browser-based applications</li>
                <li>Rate limiting based on fair use policy</li>
            </ul>
